        {
          "name": "It Proximity Mine",
          "description": "The first time your Melta Mine marker is within can perform the Pick Up Marker action on that marker, and another operative’s control range, remove that marker and inflict whenever it performs the Place Marker action on that marker, 2D6+3 damage on that operative; if it isn’t incapacitated, end it can immediately perform a free Dash action. That marker its action (if any), even if that action’s effects aren’t fulfilled. If cannot be placed within an enemy operative’s control range (if it cannot be placed, move it the minimum amount to do so. Note this operative is incapacitated while carrying that marker and that this operative is ignored for these effects (i.e. it cannot set it that marker cannot be placed, it’s removed with this operative). off or take damage from that marker)."
        },
        {
          "name": "Blast Padding",
          "description": "Whenever an operative is shooting this operative with a weapon that has the Blast or Torrent weapon rule (excluding weapons that have a sweeping profile), you can re-roll one of your defence dice. In addition, this operative isn’t affected by the x\" Devastating x weapon rule (i.e. Devastating with a distance) unless they are the target during that sequence."
        }
